===''Pokémon the Series''===
{{main|Korrina (anime)}}
Korrina is a recurring character in ''[[Pokémon the Series: XY]]'' who met {{Ash}} and {{ashfr}} in ''[[XY030|Mega Revelations!]]'' on their way to her hometown. The group accompanied her as she traveled to [[Geosenge Town]] to understand and master the [[Mega Evolution]] of her trusted partner {{TP|Korrina|Lucario}}. She left the group at [[Pomace Mountain]] in ''[[XY034|The Bonds of Mega Evolution!]]'', and eventually battled Ash in a [[Gym]] {{pkmn|battle}} in ''[[XY044|Showdown at the Shalour Gym!]]'', where Ash emerged victorious. She made later appearances in ''Pokémon the Series: XY'', and returned in ''[[Pokémon Journeys: The Series]]''.
